Çocuk hasta.

135
00:11:45.680 --> 00:11:48.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen gizledikçe daha beter olacak bu iş.

136
00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:51.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Selahattin, iç suyunu iç. Allah aşkına.

137
00:11:55.040 --> 00:11:56.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Selahattin nefes verir]

138
00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:01.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık'ın...

139
00:12:01.880 --> 00:12:06.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tarık'ın karısının görüştüğü adamı
ve karısını öldürdüğünden şüpheleniyoruz.

140
00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:09.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gerçi şüpheyi de geçti bu.

141
00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:11.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Selahattin nefes alır]

142
00:12:11.800 --> 00:12:14.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yusuf kurcaladıkça canımız sıkıldı, tabii.

143
00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:22.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bak, sen bu teşkilata 40 yıl
hizmet etmiş insansın.

144
00:12:26.160 --> 00:12:28.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aslında buraya ekip arabasıyla gelirdim.

145
00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:31.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Öyle oturup konuşmazdık da.

146
00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:34.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seninle oğlanı alır giderdim.

147
00:12:35.400 --> 00:12:38.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[nefes alır]
Sen daha iyi bilirsin bu işleri.

148
00:12:39.880 --> 00:12:42.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen de olsan öyle yaparsın, ha?

149
00:12:44.800 --> 00:12:46.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sana hürmetimden yalnız geldim.

150
00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:48.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Konuşalım diye.

151
00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:53.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yusuf dünden beri kayıp.

152
00:12:54.680 --> 00:12:59.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Konuşacağın bir şey varsa,
diyeceğin bir şey varsa de diye geldim.

153
00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:05.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
1996, İzmir.

154
00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:09.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Pınarbaşı Gazinosu.

155
00:13:11.320 --> 00:13:14.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Biz Bulgar'ın damında
boğma rakı içiyorduk seninle.

156
00:13:15.960 --> 00:13:18.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"İki el silah sesi" diye
geçtiler telsizden.

157
00:13:21.280 --> 00:13:23.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Senin karın o sıralar hamile.

158
00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O gün İstanbul'dan telefon gelmiş sana.

159
00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:27.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İlk bana söyledin.

160
00:13:28.600 --> 00:13:30.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Kızım olacak, Cevdet" dedin.

161
00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:34.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sarıldık birbirimize,
kalbinin sesini duydum senin.

162
00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:37.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sahur davulu gibi vuruyordu kalbin.

163
00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:40.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Gel," dedim. "Tophaneli ıslatalım bunu."

164
00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:43.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bulgar'ın oraya gittik.

165
00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:47.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sonra telsiz gelince kalktık.

166
00:13:47.640 --> 00:13:49.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ayakta duramıyoruz.

167
00:13:50.680 --> 00:13:54.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Gittik, gazinonun arka kapısından
dolandık. İlk cesedi gördük.

168
00:13:55.080 --> 00:13:56.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İçeriden de çığlıklar geliyor.

169
00:13:57.840 --> 00:14:00.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Deyyus bağırıyor. "Sus orospu, sus," diye.

170
00:14:01.560 --> 00:14:05.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biz daha içeri dalamadan, sıktı pezevenk.

171
00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:06.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sustu kadın.

172
00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:12.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ben böyle elimi kaldırdım.
İki yaptım, sana.

173
00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:14.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İki ceset.

174
00:14:16.840 --> 00:14:18.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mermiyi namluya sürdüm.

175
00:14:19.400 --> 00:14:22.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sonra bir çığlık daha duyduk.
Kızın biri bize doğru koşturuyor.

176
00:14:22.280 --> 00:14:25.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Kapıyı açtı, tam çıkacak,
arkadan vurdu deyyus.

177
00:14:25.880 --> 00:14:27.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kızcağız önümüze düştü.

178
00:14:27.840 --> 00:14:30.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gencecik kız. Yüzü gözü boyalı.

179
00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:33.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Üç ceset etti.

180
00:14:34.640 --> 00:14:36.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İki de telsizden; etti, beş.

181
00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:38.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mermi sayıyoruz seninle.

182
00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:41.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şarjörü boşalsın, dalacağız içeri.

183
00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:46.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sonra duyduk sesi.
Şarjörü attı, yenisini taktı puşt.

184
00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:50.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Daha kim bilir neler var yanında.

185
00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:52.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Cephaneyle gelmiş gazinoya.

186
00:14:52.280 --> 00:14:53.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rambo sanki.

187
00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:59.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Senin yüzüne baktım.
Sen taş yutmuş gibi oldun.

188
00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tabii, farkındayım. Karını düşünüyorsun.

189
00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:05.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Doğacak evladını düşünüyorsun.

190
00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:10.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İçeriden çığlıklar geliyor.

191
00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:12.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Herif sıkıyor.

192
00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:14.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biz dalsak, bize de sıkacak.

193
00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:16.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sana baktım, çenen titriyor.

194
00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:18.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Elinde makine titriyor.

195
00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:21.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dedim ki, "Selahattin, sen girme."

196
00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:23.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Sen burada dur."

197
00:15:25.120 --> 00:15:26.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben tek başıma daldım içeri.

198
00:15:27.760 --> 00:15:30.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Herif önce karnıma sıktı bir tane.

199
00:15:37.120 --> 00:15:40.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ben indirdim pezevengi.
Yerden bir tane daha sıktı.

200
00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:43.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O da buraya, sağ omzuma.

201
00:15:46.200 --> 00:15:47.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Altı ceset.

202
00:15:48.520 --> 00:15:50.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biri garson, gerisi kız.

203
00:15:50.880 --> 00:15:53.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biri daha 19 yaşında.

204
00:15:55.960 --> 00:15:59.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[nefes alır] Ben çok istedim
bir kız evladım olsun, olmadı.

205
00:16:00.760 --> 00:16:03.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Senin evladın,
analı babalı büyüsün istedim.

206
00:16:04.800 --> 00:16:07.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Allah sana evlat acısı
göstermesin Selahattin.

207
00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:10.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Allah kimseye vermesin.

208
00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:13.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şimdi suyunu iç, siktir git benim evimden.

209
00:16:14.640 --> 00:16:16.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir daha geleceksen, adam gibi gel.

210
00:16:16.640 --> 00:16:19.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kanıtla gel. Ekip arabasıyla gel.

211
00:16:20.600 --> 00:16:22.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ağzımı yoklamaya gelme.

212
00:16:23.400 --> 00:16:25.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sokarım hürmetine.

213
00:16:26.707 --> 00:16:28.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[tempolu müzik]

214
00:16:37.840 --> 00:16:42.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Selahattin derin nefes alır]

215
00:16:54.360 --> 00:16:55.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefes]

216
00:16:57.680 --> 00:16:58.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[bardak sesi]

217
00:17:02.240 --> 00:17:03.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Doğru dedin.

218
00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:05.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Kanıt yok elimde.</i>

219
00:17:05.560 --> 00:17:07.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Ama Taner sağ.</i>

220
00:17:10.360 --> 00:17:11.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Saklanıyor.</i>

221
00:17:15.102 --> 00:17:16.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[fonda tempolu müzik]

222
00:17:23.360 --> 00:17:24.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bunu ben biliyorum.

223
00:17:25.880 --> 00:17:27.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Eğer sen de biliyorsan...

224
00:17:27.800 --> 00:17:31.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
40 yıllık meslek itibarını
çöpe attın, demektir Cevdet.

225
00:17:59.160 --> 00:18:02.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[araba kapısı sesi]

226
00:18:02.960 --> 00:18:04.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[motor sesi]

227
00:18:09.720 --> 00:18:10.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[bir gıcırtı]

228
00:18:16.560 --> 00:18:17.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

229
00:18:27.960 --> 00:18:29.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

230
00:18:40.480 --> 00:18:41.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

231
00:18:46.835 --> 00:18:48.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[tempolu müzik]

232
00:19:05.800 --> 00:19:07.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Son durağa kadar durmayacağız bir daha.

233
00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:10.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-İnecekseniz...
-[Aslı] Tamam, sağ olun.

234
00:19:14.632 --> 00:19:16.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[fonda tempolu müzik]

235
00:19:27.702 --> 00:19:29.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[ani gerilim müziği]

236
00:19:39.080 --> 00:19:40.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

237
00:19:43.560 --> 00:19:45.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

238
00:19:47.153 --> 00:19:48.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[dalga sesleri]

239
00:19:54.120 --> 00:19:55.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık, neredesin oğlum?

240
00:19:58.520 --> 00:19:59.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

241
00:20:02.080 --> 00:20:03.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tarık?

242
00:20:13.680 --> 00:20:16.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[telefon çalıyor]

243
00:20:20.720 --> 00:20:21.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Efendim Feride?

244
00:20:22.680 --> 00:20:23.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Söyle kızım.

245
00:20:26.080 --> 00:20:28.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yok kızım yok, daha değil.

246
00:20:30.040 --> 00:20:31.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ama bulacağız elbet, merak etme.

247
00:20:32.920 --> 00:20:33.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He?

248
00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:37.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ama sakin ol kızım. Ben sana ne dedim. Ha?

249
00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:41.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sakin ol. Bulacağız ya.

250
00:20:42.160 --> 00:20:43.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ha?

251
00:20:43.640 --> 00:20:46.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamam. Hadi tamam artık, yapma böyle bak.

252
00:20:48.120 --> 00:20:50.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tamam ben seni arayacağım.
Araba kullanıyorum.

253
00:20:50.240 --> 00:20:53.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hadi, hadi bakalım kapat, hadi.

254
00:20:59.120 --> 00:21:00.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[oflar]

255
00:21:01.890 --> 00:21:03.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[fonda tempolu müzik]

256
00:21:11.140 --> 00:21:12.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[tempo yükseliyor]

257
00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:33.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[kapı açılır]

258
00:21:38.080 --> 00:21:39.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[vapur sesi]

259
00:21:48.680 --> 00:21:50.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[burundan nefes verir]

260
00:21:57.720 --> 00:21:59.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ya, ulan abi ya.

261
00:21:59.800 --> 00:22:00.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[damak şaklatır]

262
00:22:23.600 --> 00:22:25.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Bir yeni mesajınız var.</i>

263
00:22:25.600 --> 00:22:27.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Selam, benim. Cebin kapalı.</i>

264
00:22:28.200 --> 00:22:29.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Babanlardasın hâlâ herhalde.</i>

265
00:22:30.360 --> 00:22:34.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Neyse, çarşamba gecesi geliyorum ben.</i>
<i>Eve gelirim doğru.</i>

266
00:22:35.880 --> 00:22:39.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Sen de dönünce köyden</i>
<i>dinlersin mesajı diye bırakıyorum.</i>

267
00:22:39.480 --> 00:22:41.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Konuşalım gelince lütfen.</i>

268
00:22:42.480 --> 00:22:47.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Güzel, güzel. Eskiden yaptığımız gibi,</i>
<i>tamam mı?</i>

269
00:22:48.760 --> 00:22:49.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Ben...</i>

270
00:22:51.240 --> 00:22:53.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>...su gibi özledim seni.</i>

271
00:22:57.408 --> 00:22:58.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sakin bir müzik]

272
00:23:09.040 --> 00:23:11.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Aradığınız kişiye şu an ulaşılamıyor.</i>

273
00:23:11.320 --> 00:23:13.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Lütfen sinyal sesinden</i>
